race.comment: SECOND KNUCKLE (4) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, the latest scoring at this track over 278m. Ideally placed to take this out. PARIS DANGER (7) last start finished 4th on November 11 over 340m at Hobart behind Ducati Roy beaten 14 lengths (20.14) in a Grade 5. Looks one of the chances. BURNT DESIRES (2) turned in a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 278m behind Fishy Business (17.04) in a Grade 5. Should be in this for a long way. MORRISON'S VAN (1) can sneak into the finish.
